title: Lady Gaga Underboob At 2017 - Lady Gaga Grammys 2017
text:
Lady Gaga arrived at the Grammys tonight looking more than ready for her performance with Metallica. The singer hit the red carpet in a leather crop top (well, almost a full crop top) with spiked sleeves and underboob that deserves an award of its own. She topped off the look with leather hot pants, fishnets and over-the-knee platform boots. Seriously, have you ever seen underboob look this good?
Corbis Gaga posed with Metallica on the red carpet and fit in with the band perfectly. New lead singer alert?
